post0.title: Análise descritiva da perfomance de estudantes em um teste dos EUA

Carregando banco de dados e sua dimensão . dados = pd.read_csv('StudentsPerformance.csv') dados.shape . (1000, 8) . Visualizando as primeiras linhas do dataset . dados.head() . gender race/ethnicity parental level of education lunch test preparation course math score reading score writing score . 0 female | group B | bachelor's degree | standard | none | 72 | 72 | 74 | . 1 female | group C | some college | standard | completed | 69 | 90 | 88 | . 2 female | group B | master's degree | standard | none | 90 | 95 | 93 | . 3 male | group A | associate's degree | free/reduced | none | 47 | 57 | 44 | . 4 male | group C | some college | standard | none | 76 | 78 | 75 | .
